- Hi, chief.
- Hi.

162
00:14:47,517 --> 00:14:48,975
- Morning.
- Morning, sir.

163
00:14:49,058 --> 00:14:50,433
<i>♪ In this town-- ♪</i>

164
00:15:01,350 --> 00:15:02,767
Hi, Thalapathy!

165
00:15:07,017 --> 00:15:09,100
<i>♪ My life is in this town ♪</i>

166
00:15:09,183 --> 00:15:12,100
<i>♪ And I ain't going down-- ♪</i>

167
00:15:12,183 --> 00:15:14,058
Why isn't the temperature increasing?

168
00:15:14,142 --> 00:15:18,392
Some problem with the thermostat, sir.
I've called them the service team.

169
00:15:18,475 --> 00:15:19,683
They will visit today.

170
00:15:19,767 --> 00:15:21,558
- The cakes are ready for delivery.
- Okay.

171
00:15:21,642 --> 00:15:23,142
Can we dispatch them, sir?

172
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,558
- Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

