967
01:16:13,308 --> 01:16:14,642
Mount View Lodge.

968
01:16:14,725 --> 01:16:17,642
Come of your own accord
and admit that you're Leo.

969
01:16:21,100 --> 01:16:22,933
Sir, alcohol is not allowed.

970
01:16:34,183 --> 01:16:35,933
No alcohol!

971
01:17:08,767 --> 01:17:10,350
No alcohol.

972
01:17:30,933 --> 01:17:33,017
A friend of my friend is in Kadapa.

973
01:17:33,100 --> 01:17:37,100
I sent him a photo of the D Slash
cigarette box and got some details.

974
01:17:37,183 --> 01:17:40,725
Going by what he says,
the chap who came here

975
01:17:41,225 --> 01:17:42,558
is Antony Das.

976
01:17:44,142 --> 01:17:47,933
Once upon a time in Andhra Pradesh,
he ran a huge tobacco company.

977
01:17:48,017 --> 01:17:50,558
- After a big fire accident--
- Hold on.

978
01:17:51,267 --> 01:17:53,100
Why should I know
the life history of the guy

979
01:17:53,183 --> 01:17:57,433
who barged into my cafe
and blew cigarette smoke in my face?

980
01:17:57,517 --> 01:17:58,683
No, but this is important.

981
01:17:58,767 --> 01:18:01,183
- No, I--
- Let him complete.

982
01:18:01,350 --> 01:18:02,683
Go on, Joshy.

983
01:18:03,308 --> 01:18:06,600
Antony Das has a son named Leo.

984
01:18:07,350 --> 01:18:08,350
Okay.

985
01:18:08,558 --> 01:18:10,017
Leo Das.

986
01:18:10,142 --> 01:18:13,392
I couldn't find any details
other than his name.

987
01:18:13,475 --> 01:18:16,017
One group says that he did
something big and died.

988
01:18:16,100 --> 01:18:19,725
Another group believes he is still alive.

989
01:18:19,933 --> 01:18:22,142
He can fool this town.

990
01:18:23,808 --> 01:18:25,892
He can fool the world.

991
01:18:27,267 --> 01:18:29,850
But he can never fool me.

992
01:18:30,017 --> 01:18:33,892
In some odd way,
you have a striking resemblance to him.

993
01:18:34,058 --> 01:18:36,225
I saw his eyes.

994
01:18:36,850 --> 01:18:39,017
I know his eyes.

995
01:18:40,600 --> 01:18:41,600
It is him.

996
01:18:41,683 --> 01:18:44,308
Parthiban, you grew up
in an orphanage, right?

997
01:18:44,392 --> 01:18:48,350
- Do you remember anything from before?
- What is this? This is bullshit!

998
01:18:48,433 --> 01:18:49,808
We are the victims here.

999
01:18:49,892 --> 01:18:52,392
Do you understand you are treating
the victim like an accused?

1000
01:18:52,475 --> 01:18:54,100
- Let's leave, Parthi.
- Wait, dear.

1001
01:18:54,183 --> 01:18:55,517
Sathya, one moment.

1002
01:18:56,392 --> 01:18:57,558
Joshy.

1003
01:18:59,225 --> 01:19:02,100
I get that you are asking this
out of concern.

1004
01:19:02,475 --> 01:19:04,350
But since my childhood

1005
01:19:04,433 --> 01:19:07,517
until I was 20, I grew up
in Sathyamangalam Orphanage.

1006
01:19:08,183 --> 01:19:09,892
And I met her there--

1007
01:19:10,017 --> 01:19:11,642
What was that, dear?
That--

1008
01:19:12,183 --> 01:19:13,725
Munnar trekking.

1009
01:19:13,808 --> 01:19:15,142
There's where we met.

1010
01:19:16,183 --> 01:19:18,142
I saw her.
I got to know her.

1011
01:19:18,308 --> 01:19:20,642
Within two days,
I asked her if she'd marry me.

1012
01:19:20,725 --> 01:19:21,725
That's all.

1013
01:19:21,892 --> 01:19:25,392
After marrying her,
we settled here because of her job.

1014
01:19:25,600 --> 01:19:28,558
This has been my town since then.
This is my story.

1015
01:19:29,642 --> 01:19:31,683
They have also come
from the south, Parthiban.

1016
01:19:31,767 --> 01:19:35,350
If they've crossed so many miles
and come by road to our place

1017
01:19:35,433 --> 01:19:38,017
in search of you, something is amiss.

1018
01:19:38,267 --> 01:19:40,808
Whatever came to a grinding halt
because of him

1019
01:19:40,892 --> 01:19:43,100
needs to be completed using him.

1020
01:19:44,600 --> 01:19:47,642
I know how to bring him back
into our fold.

1021
01:19:48,183 --> 01:19:49,933
My world is very small, Joshy.

1022
01:19:50,017 --> 01:19:53,100
It's like a snow globe
that fits in the palm of my hand.

1023
01:19:53,183 --> 01:19:57,433
A small independent house,
surrounded by trees, snow, cool breeze.

1024
01:19:58,642 --> 01:20:00,350
Why is this happening to me?

1025
01:20:00,933 --> 01:20:02,933
Do you understand what I'm saying?

1026
01:20:03,142 --> 01:20:04,183
I'm sorry.

1027
01:20:05,975 --> 01:20:08,100
It's alright.
I understand.

1028
01:20:08,517 --> 01:20:10,975
If they come back
to cause further trouble,

1029
01:20:11,350 --> 01:20:12,808
we'll inform the police.

1030
01:20:12,892 --> 01:20:15,517
Keep an eye on his family and friends.

1031
01:20:15,642 --> 01:20:16,892
I'll take care of it.

1032
01:20:25,183 --> 01:20:28,225
I feel like someone
is watching our home, Sathya.

1033
01:20:29,475 --> 01:20:31,808
I don't know, Sathya.
The eerie silence

1034
01:20:32,933 --> 01:20:35,683
makes me restless.
I feel very disturbed.

1035
01:20:39,100 --> 01:20:41,808
Look here.
Understand this.

1036
01:20:42,267 --> 01:20:46,183
You should feel this way
only if I suspect you.

1037
01:20:47,683 --> 01:20:49,642
Have I ever questioned you?

1038
01:20:50,142 --> 01:20:53,600
Stop thinking about these things
and sleep peacefully, come.

1039
01:20:56,183 --> 01:20:57,558
Won't you come?

1040
01:21:00,017 --> 01:21:02,433
Okay, shall we stand like this and sleep?

1041
01:21:04,683 --> 01:21:07,267
Don't touch the engine,
just fix the heater.

1042
01:21:07,975 --> 01:21:09,225
I want my vehicle.

1043
01:21:12,808 --> 01:21:14,808
Get it ready by evening, okay?

1044
01:21:42,225 --> 01:21:43,600
What do you want?

1045
01:21:45,975 --> 01:21:47,517
I saw you, right?

1046
01:21:48,267 --> 01:21:49,517
That's enough for me.

1047
01:21:51,100 --> 01:21:54,475
I'm so mad at you, if I slap you now

1048
01:21:54,725 --> 01:21:56,350
your mouth will be injured badly

1049
01:21:56,433 --> 01:21:59,183
and it will seem like
a weird smile is plastered.

1050
01:21:59,267 --> 01:22:00,308
I'm sorry.

1051
01:22:00,475 --> 01:22:02,392
- Get out!
- I'll leave!

1052
01:22:04,808 --> 01:22:06,350
I'll leave.

1053
01:22:10,808 --> 01:22:13,308
- Tell me, dear.
- I bought the tablet you wanted, Parthi.

1054
01:22:13,392 --> 01:22:14,808
<i>Do you want anything else?</i>

1055
01:22:14,892 --> 01:22:16,475
I've given the jeep for service.

1056
01:22:16,558 --> 01:22:18,409
Didn't I tell you that we can go later
to the pharmacy?

1057
01:22:18,433 --> 01:22:22,225
- <i>Why did you leave the kid alone at home?</i>
- I brought Mathi with me.

1058
01:22:22,308 --> 01:22:23,600
<i>Priya is also with me.</i>

1059
01:22:23,683 --> 01:22:25,743
Okay. We could've waited for a day.
What was the hurry?

1060
01:22:25,767 --> 01:22:27,433
Some things can't be delayed, right?

1061
01:22:27,517 --> 01:22:29,683
<i>It's not a problem.
I'll take an auto home.</i>

1062
01:22:29,767 --> 01:22:31,409
- <i>You take care.</i>
- Okay. Go home and call me.

1063
01:22:31,433 --> 01:22:33,642
Let's go.
Come, dear.

1064
01:23:01,642 --> 01:23:02,642
No!

1065
01:23:59,308 --> 01:24:01,517
There's nothing to panic about.

1066
01:24:03,350 --> 01:24:05,183
It is the same blood.

1067
01:24:06,017 --> 01:24:07,517
Do you know who she is?

1068
01:24:08,725 --> 01:24:10,183
My granddaughter.

1069
01:24:11,100 --> 01:24:12,600
My blood.

1070
01:24:14,433 --> 01:24:16,267
Yesterday you were the one who--

1071
01:24:16,808 --> 01:24:20,183
You better leave
or I may have to call the police.

1072
01:24:21,558 --> 01:24:22,683
Police?

1073
01:24:24,475 --> 01:24:26,558
I haven't come to trouble you, dear.

1074
01:24:26,642 --> 01:24:31,308
You've been living with a guy who you
believe is Parthiban for the past 20 years

1075
01:24:31,517 --> 01:24:34,433
when you realise he was a ruthless killer

1076
01:24:34,558 --> 01:24:39,475
who committed many murders,

1077
01:24:40,017 --> 01:24:41,392
come and meet me.

1078
01:24:42,392 --> 01:24:46,183
I'll show you the true colors
of your husband.

1079
01:24:53,517 --> 01:24:55,326
- Hello?
- Why didn't you answer the call, Parthi?

1080
01:24:55,350 --> 01:24:56,910
- He was here.
- <i>What happened, Sathya?</i>

1081
01:24:56,975 --> 01:24:58,100
<i>Who?
Who was there?</i>

1082
01:24:58,183 --> 01:25:00,558
The same guy!
You said he visited the cafe yesterday!

1083
01:25:00,642 --> 01:25:02,322
<i>He came to the medical shop
looking for me.</i>

1084
01:25:02,350 --> 01:25:03,600
<i>Okay.
Where are you now?</i>

1085
01:25:03,683 --> 01:25:04,767
I am at home.

1086
01:25:04,850 --> 01:25:07,558
<i>They followed me in their car.
It is parked outside our home.</i>

1087
01:25:07,642 --> 01:25:10,267
<i>Sathya, close the doors.
Give the phone to the police officer.</i>

1088
01:25:10,350 --> 01:25:12,350
He is missing.
No one is here.

1089
01:25:12,433 --> 01:25:13,683
<i>I'm scared, Parthi.</i>

1090
01:25:13,767 --> 01:25:15,892
<i>Lock yourself in our bedroom safely.</i>

1091
01:25:15,975 --> 01:25:18,142
<i>Siddhu is coming.
I'm also on my way!</i>

1092
01:25:29,892 --> 01:25:31,267
Answer the call!

1093
01:25:31,808 --> 01:25:34,892
- Dad, what is it?
- Siddharth! Go home immediately

1094
01:25:34,975 --> 01:25:36,868
- and pick your spear and go in.
- What are you saying, Dad?

1095
01:25:36,892 --> 01:25:40,267
If anyone tries to enter the house,
throw your spear without hesitation.

1096
01:25:40,350 --> 01:25:41,600
Okay, Dad.

1097
01:27:04,808 --> 01:27:07,433
Will our lives be like this now, Parthi?

1098
01:27:07,808 --> 01:27:09,648
We have to be on the run.
Then we have to hide.

1099
01:27:09,725 --> 01:27:10,975
We should live in fear

1100
01:27:11,058 --> 01:27:14,350
wondering what might happen
to our kids. Right?

1101
01:27:15,142 --> 01:27:17,100
Tell me.
Who is he?

1102
01:27:17,225 --> 01:27:19,558
He claims that our daughter
is his granddaughter.

1103
01:27:19,642 --> 01:27:21,850
I feel terrified when I look at him.

1104
01:27:22,142 --> 01:27:25,350
We don't usually pay attention
to how our heart beats

1105
01:27:25,642 --> 01:27:28,933
but today, I could feel every beat
as I made my way home.

1106
01:27:29,642 --> 01:27:30,808
Chintu, come here.

1107
01:27:30,892 --> 01:27:33,475
Don't call her!
She's already terrified.

1108
01:27:48,975 --> 01:27:51,350
- Listen--
- I forced the police department,

1109
01:27:51,600 --> 01:27:53,392
I fought with the law,

1110
01:27:53,475 --> 01:27:54,975
and went to great lengths

1111
01:27:55,058 --> 01:27:57,017
to bring you to my doorstep.

1112
01:27:57,308 --> 01:27:59,642
I asked you to protect my family.

1113
01:27:59,725 --> 01:28:02,975
Do you possess
any integrity or job ethics?

1114
01:28:05,433 --> 01:28:06,517
Don't say that.

1115
01:28:06,600 --> 01:28:08,534
There's no use
talking about compassion or concern

1116
01:28:08,558 --> 01:28:10,725
to those who work for money.

1117
01:28:10,808 --> 01:28:12,517
Instead of doing your duty like this

1118
01:28:12,600 --> 01:28:16,100
by just eating and sleeping uselessly,
pick up your belongings and go away!

1119
01:28:16,183 --> 01:28:18,392
- Don't say that, sir.
- What?

1120
01:28:18,475 --> 01:28:20,743
- Don't act on impulse.
- Under the pretext of making excuses

1121
01:28:20,767 --> 01:28:22,808
don't provoke me to swear at you.

1122
01:28:22,892 --> 01:28:24,392
- I went to recharge--
- Don't talk.

1123
01:28:24,475 --> 01:28:25,642
Don't talk!

1124
01:28:25,725 --> 01:28:27,267
- I went to recharge--
- Don't talk!

1125
01:28:27,350 --> 01:28:29,600
I'm letting you go out of respect
for your age, or--

1126
01:28:29,683 --> 01:28:31,600
You've misunderstood me.

1127
01:28:31,683 --> 01:28:35,017
- Dear--
- Go. Just go.

1128
01:28:38,267 --> 01:28:39,267
I'm sorry, Dad.

1129
01:28:40,142 --> 01:28:43,142
- I didn't know that it was you--
- It's okay, Son.

1130
01:28:43,350 --> 01:28:44,350
Good throw.

1131
01:28:44,683 --> 01:28:47,558
- You knew it was me and threw it, right?
- No, Dad.

1132
01:28:56,808 --> 01:28:59,308
<i>When you realize
that the man sharing your bed</i>

1133
01:28:59,392 --> 01:29:02,725
<i>is a ruthless killer with no mercy,</i>

1134
01:29:03,433 --> 01:29:04,767
<i>come and meet me.</i>

1135
01:29:17,183 --> 01:29:18,183
Was it a dream?

1136
01:29:19,725 --> 01:29:21,475
It must have been a nightmare.

1137
01:29:35,725 --> 01:29:39,850
<i>I think some major conflict occurred
between the family members.</i>

1138
01:29:40,642 --> 01:29:45,475
<i>It seems this is also a reason for
their tobacco industry to get destroyed.</i>

1139
01:29:45,600 --> 01:29:47,683
<i>I have sent the certificates
and photos to you.</i>

1140
01:29:47,767 --> 01:29:50,475
I want to know if they are forged or not.
Okay? Okay, bye.

1141
01:29:50,558 --> 01:29:52,183
<i>It's a myth that stands still, Joshy.</i>

1142
01:29:52,267 --> 01:29:55,642
<i>But I believe a man who knows
the full story is alive in Shimla prison.</i>

1143
01:29:55,725 --> 01:29:58,433
<i>His name is Hridayaraj D'Souza
in the records.</i>

1144
01:29:58,517 --> 01:30:01,267
<i>If the intel is right,
he must be very close to Leo Das.</i>

1145
01:30:01,350 --> 01:30:04,350
<i>So if you want to see him,
you have only two days.</i>

1146
01:30:04,433 --> 01:30:06,683
<i>Practically, I don't know
when you can reach.</i>

1147
01:30:06,767 --> 01:30:08,493
- <i>Can I try to connect him in a call?</i>
- No--

1148
01:30:08,517 --> 01:30:10,808
I-I'm on my way,
make the arrangements, please.

1149
01:30:10,892 --> 01:30:12,058
I'll reach by tonight, okay?

1150
01:30:12,142 --> 01:30:13,017
- <i>Sure, Joshy.</i>
- Thank you.

1151
01:30:13,100 --> 01:30:15,392
<i>Who is the villain here?</i>

1152
01:30:20,058 --> 01:30:22,392
It's late.
Your mom isn't back yet.

1153
01:30:22,850 --> 01:30:25,642
Recently, she has been
returning late everyday.

1154
01:30:26,642 --> 01:30:28,600
- Isn't it?
- Yes.

1155
01:30:29,642 --> 01:30:31,142
That's her.

1156
01:30:34,100 --> 01:30:36,975
- Tell me.
- <i>Parthi, I'm not coming home tonight.</i>

1157
01:30:37,308 --> 01:30:39,108
<i>Don't wait for me.
Have your dinner and sleep.</i>

1158
01:30:39,183 --> 01:30:43,017
- Why? What happened?
- I've taken many days off, right?

1159
01:30:43,100 --> 01:30:44,725
So there's a lot of pending work.

1160
01:30:44,808 --> 01:30:47,475
I thought I'll finish it
and come home in the morning.

1161
01:30:47,558 --> 01:30:49,493
I yelled at Siddhu this morning,
so he isn't answering my call.

1162
01:30:49,517 --> 01:30:51,267
<i>Is he back home?
Where is he?</i>

1163
01:30:51,350 --> 01:30:53,683
Poor boy, I was quite harsh.
Check on him, Parthi.

1164
01:30:53,767 --> 01:30:56,167
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,
may I have your kind attention, please?</i>

1165
01:30:56,225 --> 01:30:57,850
Okay, where are you now?

1166
01:30:59,225 --> 01:31:01,808
- At the head office.
- Is that so?

1167
01:31:06,558 --> 01:31:08,433
- Chintu.
- Yes?

1168
01:31:09,600 --> 01:31:12,600
You don't suspect your dad, right?

1169
01:31:12,683 --> 01:31:14,558
- No.
- Why?

1170
01:31:14,808 --> 01:31:16,642
Because you are my dearest dad.

1171
01:31:17,767 --> 01:31:19,558
Your dearest dad.

1172
01:31:28,767 --> 01:31:30,350
Hey! It's your dad.

1173
01:31:31,225 --> 01:31:32,892
Siddharth, get into the car!

1174
01:31:36,642 --> 01:31:39,392
- I'm calling you, get into--
- Let go of my hand!

1175
01:31:43,100 --> 01:31:45,558
Sir, leave him alone
if he doesn't want to come.

1176
01:31:45,642 --> 01:31:46,683
Don't force him.

1177
01:31:47,225 --> 01:31:49,100
What?
Will you kill him too?

1178
01:31:56,725 --> 01:31:58,183
Okay, don't come.

1179
01:32:08,308 --> 01:32:10,225
<i>♪ Who is the villain here? ♪</i>

1180
01:32:10,600 --> 01:32:12,517
<i>♪ Who is the friend, dear and near? ♪</i>

1181
01:32:12,933 --> 01:32:14,933
<i>♪ Who is the villain in the end? ♪</i>

1182
01:32:15,142 --> 01:32:16,933
<i>♪ Who is the friend and godsend? ♪</i>

1183
01:32:17,017 --> 01:32:20,183
If I see any of you
following my family hereafter--

1184
01:32:20,267 --> 01:32:21,850
Hey! Go with your dad.

1185
01:32:21,933 --> 01:32:24,100
<i>♪ Who is the villain here? ♪</i>

1186
01:32:28,642 --> 01:32:30,475
- Sir.
- Why are you sitting here

1187
01:32:30,558 --> 01:32:33,225
in the cold at this hour?
No intruder will barge in now.

1188
01:32:33,308 --> 01:32:36,058
I don't care anymore who shoots
and who dies, go to sleep.

1189
01:32:36,142 --> 01:32:37,642
It's okay.
It's okay, sir.

1190
01:32:37,725 --> 01:32:40,975
A courier was delivered in the noon
in your wife's name.

1191
01:32:41,600 --> 01:32:44,392
Sir, one moment.
I wanted to tell you something.

1192
01:32:45,100 --> 01:32:47,975
I understand all your worries and fears.

1193
01:32:48,225 --> 01:32:52,933
I see how well you take care
of the people who depend on you.

1194
01:32:53,267 --> 01:32:55,659
You are anxious and upset
that something might happen to them.

1195
01:32:55,683 --> 01:32:57,350
I'll retire in 60 days.

1196
01:32:57,558 --> 01:33:01,933
If anyone troubles your family
in any way during this time,

1197
01:33:02,600 --> 01:33:04,308
I'll take him down with me!

1198
01:33:04,392 --> 01:33:08,183
Even if there is any emergency
needing my attention back home

1199
01:33:08,267 --> 01:33:10,100
I won't leave this place.

1200
01:33:11,350 --> 01:33:14,683
I swear this Napoleon doesn't work
just to eat like a glutton, sir.

1201
01:33:14,767 --> 01:33:18,475
I don't work just to fill my stomach.
Trust me, sir.

1202
01:33:25,892 --> 01:33:28,642
